It's been two years since we first met, and it's been a year since we work and walk together.
This year have been a very special year to me, i have met this 4 people which i share the same goal, the same vision and the same mission for our loveable club.
There has been some hard time sure, time when we argue, cried, laughed, stressed, concerned and fought together. It has been a roller coaster ride for sure, but i never regret and thankful for meeting and working with you guys.
Thanks for all the memories and happiness we've been through together, you guys are my precious friends and team mates and let's do our best in each of our future!!! :))
